&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-end delivery ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Define and manage schedule, scope, and budget across technical and non-technical workstreams, from initiation through go-live and hypercare.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder liaison:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary point of contact between project sponsors, business stakeholders, and delivery teams, balancing competing priorities with clarity and transparency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Planning:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and maintain detailed project plans, RAID logs, resource plans, and dependency maps; surface risks proactively before they become blockers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Progress tracking and reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor milestones and performance metrics; provide regular status updates to leadership, including executive-level reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
