&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the VP, Strategy, the Senior Manager, Strategy will be a core member of a lean, high-impact team driving strategic priorities across Kensington Tours and the broader Range Travel portfolio. This is a generalist strategy role, and requires rigorous analysis, structured problem-solving, and executive communication. You will support strategic projects from framing through to recommendation, support enterprise-level planning, and build trusted relationships with senior leaders across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
