&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and drive the editorial calendar and publishing cadence for Kensington&#39;s travel intelligence newsletters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI to curate and synthesize content from leading travel trade and consumer publications into a coherent weekly briefing across regions and travel categories that inform and inspire.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and write the editorial view that layers Kensington&#39;s expert perspective onto curated stories across digital channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and iterate on newsletter layout and templates, including sections for breaking travel news, regional updates, product spotlights, and partner integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trust &amp;amp; Credibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build source relationships with travel publications; negotiate content-sharing arrangements that benefit both parties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish editorial standards, style and editorial tone that position Kensington as the credible, trusted authoritative voice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain clear separation between news judgment and commercial interests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate unlocked insight from Kensington&#39;s Destination Expert and Kensington team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance &amp;amp; Iteration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in leading structured A/B testing to determine what formats and stories drive optimal engagement, sales leads and KPI achievement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track reader behaviour and feedback to continuously sharpen editorial&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze, report and present to leadership on newsletter performance, your optimizations and its direct impact on leads and travel bookings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
